{"tid":2184582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Luke De Pulford眾籌告英藉港黑警 達標!!! 感謝4547位手足!!","createTime":"2020-09-01T15:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T05:51:31.000Z","uid":267556,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8f56d40d23e0f452933f75e05a04c731e2daa843","tid":2184582,"uid":267556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:41:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1300763193044852737\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1300763193044852737&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=0795d677\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1300763193044852737&h=bce18271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1300763193044852737</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.justgiving.com/crowdfunding/justiceforhongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justgiving.com%2Fcrowdfunding%2Fjusticeforhongkong&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=f4883c59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.justgiving.com/crowdfunding/justiceforhongkong</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>多謝所有出POST, 推POST, 捐款的手足~  香港已經淪陷, 三權分立都消失埋, 真相難以發現, 暫時, 希望公義在英國都得以彰顯!!!</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>可能 未必可以直接懲戒到班英藉港黑警~ <br />\n但我覺得有以下效果<br />\n1. 佢地唔敢返英國, 返英國會被罰, 等佢永遠共享大灣區榮耀<br />\n2. 會有証人上庭作証, 有影片物証, 會寫入判詞, 起碼有個國家正式就住香港警暴 有份官方文件 同 歷史文獻.<br />\n3. 判詞一定好精采~<br />\n4. 香港暫時仲算係Common Law, 英國的判例有參考價值. 香港的法官, 律師可以quote黎用!<br />\n5. 報紙必定會報~ 可能係幾個國家都會報.<br />\n6. 我地一直都被打壓, 一直被打, 就係得美國制裁果兩件黑警局長. 拉多幾件落黎制裁佢地!!<br />\n<br />\n一齊集氣~~~~</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im